of their relationship to life.

00:08:53.470 --> 00:08:57.245 align:middle line:84%
It was a heroic, incredibly
difficult process.

00:08:57.245 --> 00:08:59.890 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:08:59.890 --> 00:09:02.260 align:middle line:84%
For the purpose of
modern westerners,

00:09:02.260 --> 00:09:04.810 align:middle line:84%
