stones that exemplifies

00:09:04.810 --> 00:09:07.960 align:middle line:84%
the alchemical process,
and they are totally safe.

00:09:07.960 --> 00:09:11.140 align:middle line:84%
In Western mineralogy,
they are termed chalcedony.

00:09:11.140 --> 00:09:14.260 align:middle line:84%
But in Chinese thinking,
they are the agates, jaspers,

00:09:14.260 --> 00:09:16.610 align:middle line:90%
and chalcedonies.

00:09:16.610 --> 00:09:19.670 align:middle line:84%
The alchemical practice
has specific stages.

00:09:19.670 --> 00:09:21.680 align:middle line:90%
First, there is initiation.

00:09:21.680 --> 00:09:24.710 align:middle line:84%
We realize there is a
problem in our life.

00:09:24.710 --> 00:09:28.550 align:middle line:84%
Some spark of inspiration
comes, whether from a book

00:09:28.550 --> 00:09:31.220 align:middle line:84%
or a teacher, that
causes us to commit

00:09:31.220 --> 00:09:35.030 align:middle line:84%
to the formidable discipline
to really want to change.

00:09:35.030 --> 00:09:37.940 align:middle line:84%
We become aware of all
the ways we hurt ourselves

00:09:37.940 --> 00:09:40.520 align:middle line:84%
with our habits of
food or exercise,

00:09:40.520 --> 00:09:43.280 align:middle line:84%
with our habits of
thinking and beliefs,

00:09:43.280 --> 00:09:45.500 align:middle line:90%
with our habits of relationship.

00:09:45.500 --> 00:09:48.170 align:middle line:84%
This process is called the
separation of the clear

00:09:48.170 --> 00:09:49.970 align:middle line:90%
from the turbid.

00:09:49.970 --> 00:09:51.770 align:middle line:90%
Agates show us this process.

00:09:51.770 --> 00:09:55.130 align:middle line:84%
They have bands or
specks or other patterns

00:09:55.130 --> 00:09:58.070 align:middle line:84%
showing how different minerals
have separated themselves

00:09:58.070 --> 00:10:00.030 align:middle line:90%
from the others.

00:10:00.030 --> 00:10:03.630 align:middle line:84%
As we do this separation,
we find areas of blockage.

00:10:03.630 --> 00:10:06.540 align:middle line:84%
We just can't let go
of a particular habit.

00:10:06.540 --> 00:10:09.120 align:middle line:90%
We have to purify it out of us.

00:10:09.120 --> 00:10:12.360 align:middle line:84%
For this part of the
process, we can use jasper.

00:10:12.360 --> 00:10:14.340 align:middle line:84%
From the Chinese
point of view, jasper

00:10:14.340 --> 00:10:17.490 align:middle line:84%
