or make an elixir from it.

00:10:24.450 --> 00:10:27.300 align:middle line:84%
Purification takes a
long time, and things

00:10:27.300 --> 00:10:28.680 align:middle line:90%
change along the way.

00:10:28.680 --> 00:10:31.890 align:middle line:84%
Fortunately, jasper offers
us choices along the way.

00:10:31.890 --> 00:10:34.650 align:middle line:84%
We can use red,
yellow, green, brown

00:10:34.650 --> 00:10:39.210 align:middle line:84%
to help us clear out all the
various blockages we encounter.

00:10:39.210 --> 00:10:41.520 align:middle line:84%
When we're cleared
out of everything,

00:10:41.520 --> 00:10:44.280 align:middle line:84%
it's time for refinement
and stability.

00:10:44.280 --> 00:10:46.440 align:middle line:84%
It's all well and
good to do this work

00:10:46.440 --> 00:10:49.800 align:middle line:84%
in the privacy of your
home, your meditation space.

00:10:49.800 --> 00:10:51.900 align:middle line:84%
But then you go into
the world, and what

00:10:51.900 --> 00:10:54.510 align:middle line:84%
you thought was a stability
of your refinement

00:10:54.510 --> 00:10:55.950 align:middle line:90%
flies out the window.

00:10:55.950 --> 00:10:57.930 align:middle line:90%
It's time for more work.

00:10:57.930 --> 00:11:00.150 align:middle line:90%
Now, we use the chalcedonies.

00:11:00.150 --> 00:11:04.380 align:middle line:84%
These are also single color
stones, no bands or specks,

00:11:04.380 --> 00:11:06.480 align:middle line:90%
